  "prompt": "What are some good real estate agencies in ahmedabad?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, several reputable real estate agencies operate in Ahmedabad. While specific agency performance may vary based on your needs (buying, selling, renting, commercial properties, etc.), here are some well-known real estate agencies in the area:\n\n1. **Nirmaan Group** - Known for both residential and commercial real estate services and offers a range of properties in Ahmedabad.\n\n2. **Homeland Realty** - Offers services ranging from residential to commercial real estate, specializing in properties throughout Ahmedabad.\n\n3. **Shreeji Realty** - Focuses on residential properties and has a good reputation for customer service and market knowledge.\n\n4. **Rajdeep Real Estate** - Offers a wide variety of property options and is known for honest dealings in residential and commercial properties.\n\n5. **Globe Real Estate** - Provides a comprehensive range of real estate services and has a solid understanding of the local market.\n\n6. **Apex Realty** - Specializes in both residential and commercial properties, offering buying, selling, and leasing services.\n\n7. **Sentinel Properties** - Engaged in various real estate sectors, including residential, commercial, and investment properties.\n\n8. **Sanghvi Groups** - Known for both residential and commercial developments and also offers brokerage services.\n\n9. **Prosper Realty** - Offers property management and real estate consultancy, catering to a diverse clientele.\n\n10. **Pristine Realty** - Focuses on high-end residential properties and has experience in luxury real estate.\n\nWhen choosing a real estate agency, it's advisable to check reviews, ask for referrals, and meet with agents to discuss your specific needs. Additionally, local online listings and platforms can provide updated information and options.",
